  <summary date="2019-12-13T22:57:19Z" status="Introduced in House">IoT Readiness Act of 2019

This bill requires the Federal Communications Commission to ascertain the amount of spectrum necessary to meet rising demand by studying the growing usage of Internet of Things devices, which use a network to communicate and share data with other devices, and devices that utilize 5G networks.</summary>
